  <li>List VMs: <code class="highlighter-rouge">esxcli vm process list</code></li>
  <li>Force Shutdown: <code class="highlighter-rouge">esxcli vm process kill --type=force --world-id=&lt;$WORLD_ID&gt;</code></li>
